Hongji Jiang

Class Schedule

Stat463

Stat463 is one of the major requirment course for applied statistic. This course talks about the time series, which mainly focus on the white noise of the model. The psu canvas page are here(https://psu.instructure.com/courses/2040943)

1

Egee101

In this course, we study about the energy usage and generation in our society. Transportation is the largest consumer engergy use. The psu canvas page are here(https://psu.instructure.com/courses/2023105)

3

Earth101

This class mainly focus on the disasters such as earthquake, tsunami, and conflagration. In this cource, we are discussing and learning the damage and restore from these disaster by looking at their attributes. The psu canvas page are here(https://psu.instructure.com/courses/2023078)
